mixed choir'' Op.&nbsp;74 (1972)<ref>{{cite AV media |people=Chamber Choir of the Feliks Nowowiejski Academy of Music |date=29 August 2017 |title=OCF: AWARD \u2033Tomislav Zografski\u2033 |language=Macedonian |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ao3ik2CuXdw |access-date=1 April 2020 |format= Video |location=Diamond Hall of Hotel Inex, Ohrid, Republic of Macedonia |publisher=YouTube}}</ref>\n* ''Allegro barrocco'' for two violins and piano (1973)<ref>{{cite web | title=Review of Composers \u2013 Composers' Association of Serbia |url=http://composers.rs/en/?page_id=994|website=www.composers.rs|access-date=2020-01-22}}</ref>\n* Passacaglia, symphonic poem (1981)<ref name=\"Foundation1\" />\n* ''Essay On The Rain'' \u2014 song cycle for voice and piano (1982)<ref>{{cite web | title=Tomislav Zografski album|url=https://www.discogs.com/%D0%A2%D0%BE%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B2-%D0%97%D0%BE%D0%B3%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%84%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8-Tomislav-Zografski/release/5825066|website=www.discogs.com|access-date=2020-01-26}}</ref>\n* Song for solo violin, Op.&nbsp;101 (1983)<ref name=\"CompToday1\">{{cite web | title=List of Works|url=http://www.compositiontoday.com/composers/785.asp|website=www.compositiontoday.com|access-date=2020-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Zografski|first1=Tomislav|title=Song for Solo Violin |url=http://ohridskibiseri.org.mk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Zografski_op.101__song_for_violina_solo__1983_orig.pdf|website=www.ohridskibiseri.org.mk/|publisher=Tomislav Zografski Foundation}}</ref>\n* ''Songs for Jakshini'' for voice and piano (1983)<ref name=\"Foundation2\" /><ref name=\"Blesok1\" />\n* Scherzo for symphony orchestra (1985)<ref name=\"Blesok1\" />\n* Rhapsody for violin and piano, Op.&nbsp;103<ref name=\"Foundation2\" />\n* Sonata for two pianos, Op.&nbsp;122 (1990)\n* Skherzo (1991)<ref name=\"Foundation1\" />\n* Five pieces for clarinet, Op.&nbsp;131 (1997)<ref name=\"Ohrid1\" />\n* ''Compositions'' for viola and violin, violin and piano\n* 